Holly Aird https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Holly_Aird 0 Imogen Holly Aird (born 18 May 1969) is an English television actress known for playing Forensic Pathologist Frankie Wharton in the BBC1 drama series Waking the Dead, having previously starred in productions such as Soldier Soldier and the 1997 film Fever Pitch alongside Colin Firth.
